compat-change.description: With RADIO_U_VERSION_REQUIRED enabled, 44-bit DAB identifier {@code IdentifierType#DAB_SID_EXT} from broadcast radio HAL can be passed as {@code ProgramSelector#IDENTIFIER_TYPE_DAB_DMB_SID_EXT} to {@code RadioTuner}.
compat-change.name: RADIO_U_VERSION_REQUIRED

compat-change.description: With RADIO_V_VERSION_REQUIRED enabled, identifier types, config flags and metadata added in V for HD radio can be passed to {@code RadioTuner} by {@code android.hardware.radio.ITunerCallback}
compat-change.name: RADIO_V_VERSION_REQUIRED
